54:42.879 --> 54:46.950
Will you be reunited

54:46.951 --> 54:49.184
with your loved ones?

54:49.586 --> 54:53.156
That is his question to me.

54:53.157 --> 54:57.627
You are fooling yourself.

54:57.628 --> 54:59.529
But truthfully,

54:59.530 --> 55:03.398
I've asked myself
that a hundred times.

55:05.435 --> 55:07.068
I don't know.

55:12.742 --> 55:16.311
I've not known the answer,

55:16.946 --> 55:19.214
for a very long time.

55:24.654 --> 55:27.057
The scar in your mind,

55:27.058 --> 55:28.858
and on your face,

55:28.859 --> 55:31.895
will never attract the eyes,

55:31.896 --> 55:35.430
especially the heart of another.

55:36.099 --> 55:38.835
- My
hope comes and goes,

55:38.836 --> 55:41.104
as often as they do.

55:41.105 --> 55:45.173
I am fully aware,

55:47.310 --> 55:49.845
I'm not the same person.

55:56.986 --> 55:59.089
But is that terrible?

55:59.090 --> 56:02.390
Am I worse than I was?

56:03.326 --> 56:07.597
Or just different,
with all that I know,

56:07.598 --> 56:10.033
about the truth and the stars?

56:10.034 --> 56:14.369
But I have become better,

56:15.538 --> 56:17.305
because of it.

56:18.508 --> 56:22.412
Their blood may course
through my veins,

56:22.413 --> 56:24.547
but so does mine.

56:24.548 --> 56:30.186
It's still my brain that
moves my arms, my legs,

56:30.187 --> 56:33.955
gives my heart love,
as well as anger.

56:34.524 --> 56:39.996
There is nothing
irrelevant to emotion.

56:39.997 --> 56:43.333
Everything we do in
life is tied to it.

56:43.334 --> 56:47.003
It isn't learned,
it is part of us.

56:47.004 --> 56:50.807
It can build us up,
it can destroy us.

56:50.808 --> 56:53.910
It can do both,
with no intervention.

56:53.911 --> 56:58.481
It truly is
emotion that is driving
me to finish them off.

56:58.482 --> 57:01.117
No one will understand,

57:01.118 --> 57:05.021
nor tolerate your
past conflicts.

57:05.022 --> 57:08.124
- He
was wrong on one thing.

57:08.125 --> 57:10.794
It is not anger,

57:10.795 --> 57:13.062
it is not hope,

57:13.063 --> 57:16.299
it is for the love
i keep buried,

57:16.300 --> 57:20.570
love of nature, people,

57:20.571 --> 57:24.040
the spring blossoms that
are over my head now,

57:24.041 --> 57:26.176
to watch the sunset,

57:26.177 --> 57:30.780
and wonder, childlike, as to
where the sun goes each night,

57:30.781 --> 57:33.950
a pure passion to actually live,

57:33.951 --> 57:37.387
to go through life learning
about things around me,

57:37.388 --> 57:41.024
without needing to
know everything,

57:41.025 --> 57:43.124
or every outcome.

57:44.794 --> 57:48.630
What will you gain?

57:52.335 --> 57:54.636
What will you gain?

57:58.341 --> 58:01.578
The freedom from

58:01.579 --> 58:02.911
knowledge.

58:06.583 --> 58:10.019
Freedom to progress as I desire,

58:10.020 --> 58:12.422
not forced to progress.

58:12.423 --> 58:15.158
The choice to sleep
without memories,

58:15.159 --> 58:17.026
and wake without fear,

58:17.027 --> 58:22.599
the confidence that
what happens for me,

58:22.600 --> 58:24.499
and the future,

58:25.168 --> 58:30.071
it's driven by,

58:32.709 --> 58:34.075
me.

